PrecisRe-appointment of SYLVIE LÉVESQUE, of Outremont, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective April 20, 2001.
